(190, '_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'https://wordpress.org/news/2015/04/improvements-to-wordpress-org/\'>Improvements to WordPress.org</a> <span class="rss-date">April 4, 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">If you visit WordPress.org regularly you might have noticed some changes around the place. If you don’t, now’s the time to check them out! We’ve been working hard to improve the site to make it more useful to everyone, both developers and users, and we hope you like what we’ve done. New Theme and Plugin Directories [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://ma.tt/2015/04/alcohol-or-marijuana/\'>Matt: Alcohol or Marijuana?</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://ma.tt/2015/04/9-truths-computer-programmers-know/\'>Matt: 9 Truths Computer Programmers know</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wptavern.com/pressthis-revamped-with-a-new-user-interface-and-minimalist-design\'>WPTavern: PressThis Revamped with a New User Interface and Minimalist Design</a></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
