e: <a title="How to Customize Default Places Bar in Windows Common File Dialog Box?" href="http://www.askvg.com/how-to-customize-default-places-bar-in-windows-common-file-dialog-box/" target="_blank">How to Customize Default Places Bar in Windows Common File Dialog Box?</a></em>', 'Personalizar Favoritos en el Cuadro de Diálogo Común', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-04-06 09:10:07', '2015-04-06 09:10:07', '', 3, 'http://pcadvice.co.nf/es/2015/04/06/3-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
