(353, 1, '2015-03-24 20:57:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<ul>\r\n<li>list item one</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>list item two paragraph one</p>\r\n<p>list item two paragraph two</p>\r\n<p>list item two paragraph three</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'test', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2015-03-24 20:57:50', '2015-03-24 20:57:50', '', 0, 'http://pcadvice.co.nf/?p=353', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(361, 1, '2015-03-24 21:22:27', '2015-03-24 21:22:27', '<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-363" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/chckdsk-screen.jpg" alt="Check Disk Screen" width="483" height="296" /></p>\r\n<p>1. <strong>Win+R -&gt; "regedit".</strong></p>\r\n<p>2. Find the branch:</p>\r\n<pre>HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Session Manager</pre>\r\n<p>3. Change the "<strong>BootExecute</strong>" key:</p>\r\n<pre>autocheck autochk /k:C *</pre>\r\n<p>to disable <strong>chkdsk</strong> on the <strong>C drive</strong>,</p>\r\n<pre>autocheck autochk *</pre>\r\n<p>to restore.</p>\r\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-362" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/chckdsk-reg.jpg" alt="Check Disk Registry" width="656" height="110" /></p>\r\n<p>4. Restart.</p>', 'Disable Check Disk on Startup', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'disable-check-disk-on-startup', '', '', '2015-03-24 21:22:27', '2015-03-24 21:22:27', '', 0, 'http://pcadvice.co.nf/?p=361', 0, 'post', '', 0),
