(431, 1, '2015-03-26 19:47:58', '2015-03-26 19:47:58', '<p>1. Download the program <a href="http://rammichael.com/downloads/7tt_setup.exe" target="_blank">7+ Taskbar Tweaker</a>.</p>\r\n<p>2. <strong>Install</strong> it and run.</p>\r\n<p>3. In the<strong> Middle click</strong> section select <strong>Close</strong>.</p>\r\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-434" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/taskbar-tweaker-middle-click.jpg" alt="Taskbar Tweaker middle click" width="240" height="217" /></p>\r\n<p>4. Now when pressing <strong>Wheel</strong> on <strong>Taskbar</strong> items the appropriate windows will close.</p>', 'Close Windows with Mousewheel', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'close-windows-with-mousewheel', '', '', '2015-04-04 06:05:53', '2015-04-04 06:05:53', '', 0, 'http://pcadvice.co.nf/?p=431', 0, 'post', '', 0),
