(488, 1, '2015-03-28 20:25:18', '2015-03-28 20:25:18', '1. <strong>Win+R -&gt; "diskmgmt.msc"</strong>.\r\n\r\n2. Rightclick a drive.\r\n\r\n3. Select <strong>Change Drive Letter and Paths</strong>.\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-490" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/change-drive-letter-diskmgmt.jpg" alt="Dhange drive letter diskmgmt" width="361" height="411" />\r\n\r\n4. Press <strong>Change</strong>.\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-489" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/change-drive-dialog.jpg" alt="Change drive dialog" width="577" height="453" />', 'Change Drive Letter', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'change-drive-letter', '', '', '2015-03-28 20:25:19', '2015-03-28 20:25:19', '', 0, 'http://pcadvice.co.nf/?p=488', 0, 'post', '', 0),
