(510, 1, '2015-03-28 21:31:46', '2015-03-28 21:31:46', '1. Download and install the <strong>Toddler Keys</strong> program from <a href="http://www.softpedia.com/get/Security/Lockdown/Toddler-Keys.shtml" target="_blank">here</a> or <a href="http://download.cnet.com/Toddler-Keys/3000-27064_4-10305344.html" target="_blank">here</a>.\r\n\r\n2. <strong>Open</strong> it.\r\n\r\n3. <strong>Rightclick</strong> the tray icon.\r\n\r\n4. Select<strong> Lock Keyboard</strong>.\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-511" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/lock-kbd.jpg" alt="Lock Keyboard Toddler Keys" width="243" height="199" />', 'Lock Keyboard', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'lock-keyboard', '', '', '2015-04-06 07:54:44', '2015-04-06 07:54:44', '', 0, 'http://pcadvice.co.nf/?p=510', 0, 'post', '', 0),
