(687, 1, '2015-03-31 17:54:25', '2015-03-31 17:54:25', '<p>To cast field type use these steps: </p>\r\n<h6>1. Set <code>meta_key</code> within a <strong>custom query</strong> </h6>\r\n<pre class="code-php">$query-&gt;set(\'meta_key\',\'custom_field\');</pre>\r\n<p>or </p>\r\n<pre class="code-php">$args = array(\r\n    \'meta_key\' =&gt; \'custom_field\',\r\n);</pre>\r\n<h6>2. Set <code>meta_type</code> to <em>"numeric"</em> </h6>\r\n<pre class="code-php">$query-&gt;set(\'meta_type\',\'numeric\');</pre>\r\n<p>or </p>\r\n<pre class="code-php">$args = array(\r\n    \'meta_type\' =&gt; \'numeric\',\r\n);</pre>\r\n<h6>3. This will allow you to add <strong>ordering</strong> for <strong>numeric</strong> values </h6>\r\n<pre class="code-php">$query-&gt;set( \'orderby\', "custom_field" );</pre>\r\n<p>or </p>\r\n<pre class="code-php">$args = array(\r\n    \'orderby\' =&gt; \'custom_field\',\r\n);</pre>', 'Sort Custom Query by Numeric Field', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sort-custom-query-by-numeric-field', '', '', '2015-03-31 17:54:25', '2015-03-31 17:54:25', '', 0, 'http://pcadvice.co.nf/?p=687', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(690, 1, '2015-03-31 17:57:53', '2015-03-31 17:57:53', '<p>1. To copy data <em>from</em> an <strong>Excel</strong> table <em>to</em> <strong>HTML</strong> format copy cells from a <em>.xls</em> sheet and press <strong>Ctrl+V</strong> in <em>Visual mode</em> of the <strong>Wordpress editor</strong>. The <em>HTML mode</em> will show the data in the <strong>&lt;table&gt;</strong> tags. </p>\r\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-691" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/copy-from-excel.png" alt="Copy from Excel" width="602" height="200" /></p>\r\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-693" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/copy-from-excel-wp-visual.png" alt="Copy from Excel WP Visual mode" width="743" height="527" /></p>\r\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-692" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/copy-from-excel-wp-html.png" alt="Copy from Excel WP HTML mode" width="757" height="474" /></p>', 'Wordpress Tips', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'wordpress-tips', '', '', '2015-03-31 17:57:53', '2015-03-31 17:57:53', '', 0, 'http://pcadvice.co.nf/?p=690', 0, 'post', '', 0),
