(770, 1, '2015-04-02 06:33:35', '2015-04-02 06:33:35', '<p>1. Go to <strong>C:\\xampp\\mysql\\bin</strong></p>\r\n<p>2. Add the lines to the <strong>my.ini</strong> file</p>\r\n<pre>character-set-server=utf8\r\ncollation-server=utf8_general_ci</pre>\r\n<p>in the section</p>\r\n<pre>[mysqld]</pre>\r\n<p>3. <strong>Restart</strong> the MySQL server.</p>\r\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-771" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/mysql-default-charset-heidi-result.png" alt="MySQL default charset Heidi result" width="323" height="256" /></p>', 'MySQL - Set Default Database Charset', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'mysql-set-default-database-charset', '', '', '2015-04-04 06:13:16', '2015-04-04 06:13:16', '', 0, 'http://pcadvice.co.nf/?p=770', 0, 'post', '', 0),
