(778, 1, '2015-04-02 13:53:23', '2015-04-02 13:53:23', '<p>1. Go to <strong>C:\\Windows\\system32\\drivers\\etc</strong> folder and add this line to the <strong>hosts</strong> file</p>\r\n<pre>127.0.0.1 thesite.lcom</pre>\r\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-780" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/virtual-host-hosts-file.png" alt="Virtual host Apache, hosts file" width="550" height="288" /></p>\r\n<p>2. Go to  <strong>C:\\xampp\\apache\\conf\\extra\\</strong> and add this to the file <strong>httpd-vhosts.conf</strong></p>\r\n<pre class="code">NameVirtualHost *\r\n\r\n<span class="tag">&lt;VirtualHost *&gt;</span>\r\n  DocumentRoot "C:\\xampp\\htdocs"\r\n  ServerName localhost\r\n<span class="tag">&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="tag">&lt;VirtualHost *&gt;</span>\r\n  DocumentRoot "C:\\Documents\\sites\\shop"\r\n  ServerName thesite.lcom\r\n  \r\n<span class="tag">  &lt;Directory "C:\\Documents\\sites\\shop"&gt;</span>\r\n    Require all granted\r\n<span class="tag">  &lt;/Directory&gt;</span>\r\n<span class="tag">&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</span></pre>\r\n<pre>DocumentRoot - path to the local site folder\r\nServerName - the local server custom name (from the hosts file)\r\nRequire all granted - grant access to the site through the local server</pre>\r\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-779" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/virtual-host-apache-conf.png" alt="Virtual host Apache, conf folder" width="534" height="476" /></p>\r\n<p>3. <strong>Restart</strong> the <em>Apache server</em></p>\r\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-781" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/virtual-host-server-restart.png" alt="Virtual host Apache, server restart" width="489" height="201" /></p>\r\n<p>4. Type the <strong>URL</strong> in a browser</p>\r\n<pre>thesite.lcom</pre>\r\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-782" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/virtual-host-type-url.png" alt="Virtual host Apache, type URL" width="676" height="174" /></p>', 'Virtual Host in XAMPP', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'virtual-host-in-xampp', '', '', '2015-04-02 13:53:23', '2015-04-02 13:53:23', '', 0, 'http://pcadvice.co.nf/?p=778', 0, 'post', '', 0),
