(820, 1, '2015-04-03 11:26:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<h3>Web Applications</h3>\r\n<h4>1. Torrents</h4>\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mobilityflow.torrent"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-atorrent.png" alt="" />\r\naTorrent </a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bittorrent.client"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-bittorrent.png" alt="" />\r\nBitTorrent </a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.utorrent.client"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-utorrent.png" alt="" />\r\nuTorrent </a>\r\n<h4>2. Browsers</h4>\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.mozilla.firefox"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-firefox.png" alt="" />\r\nFirefox </a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.UCMobile.intl"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-ucbrowser.png" alt="" />\r\nUC Browser </a>\r\n<h4>3. Other</h4>\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.carl.trafficcounter"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-traffic-counter.png" alt="" />\r\nTraffic Counter </a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.google.android.apps.docs"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-gdrive.png" alt="" />\r\nGoogle Drive </a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://68.233.228.211/tubemate/youtube-tubemate.2.95.apk"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-tube-mate.png" alt="" />\r\nTubeMate </a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://m.downloadatoz.com/apps/com.shimba.android.video,875047/downloading.html"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015