ice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-fora.png" alt="" />\r\nFora Dictionary </a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.suvorov.multitran"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-multitran-1.png" alt="" />\r\nMultitran Russian Dictionary </a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.vorotnikov.egor.multitran"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-multitran-2.png" alt="" />\r\nОнлайн Словарь Мультитран </a>\r\n\r\n2. English\r\n\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.funeasylearn.english"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-learn-eng-words.png" alt="" />\r\nLearn English 6,000 Words </a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=andrei.brusentcov.languagetutor.en"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-eng-lessons.png" alt="" />\r\nEnglish Lessons </a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.muth.android.conjugator_demo_en"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-eng-verbs.png" alt="" />\r\nEnglish Verbs </a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.muth.android.trainer_demo_en"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-eng-verb-trainer.png" alt="" />\r\nEnglish Verb Trainer </a>\r\n\r\n3. Spanish\r\n\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.funeasylearn.spanish"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-learn-span-words.png" alt="" />\r\nLearn Spanish 6,000 Words </a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.voclab.voclabv2spa"> <img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-learn-span-flashcards.png" alt="" />\r\nLearn Spanish Flashcards 