//play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dekovir.pixwords">PixWords</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="app-item">\r\n<div class="app-cover"><a title="Da Vinci Riddles: Mystery" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.planemo.daVinciRu"><img class="android-icon" src="http://pcadvice.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/a-da-vinci-riddles.png" alt="" /></a></div>\r\n<div class="app-name"><a title="Da Vinci Riddles: Mystery" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.planemo.daVinciRu">Da Vinci Riddles: Mystery</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'My Android Games', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'my-android-games', '', '', '2015-04-04 07:35:52', '2015-04-04 07:35:52', '', 0, 'http://pcadvice.co.nf/?p=954', 0, 'post', '', 0),
