google.com.ua/search?q=world&amp;tbs=isz:ex,iszw:3000,iszh:2000&amp;tbm=isch" target="_blank"><strong>Image</strong></a> after search.</td>\r\n<td><a href="https://www.google.com.ua/search?q=world+imagesize%3A3000x2000" target="_blank"><code><strong>world imagesize:3000x2000</strong></code></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><code><strong>filetype:</strong></code></td>\r\n<td>Search for a specific file type.</td>\r\n<td><a href="https://www.google.com.ua/search?q=waterfalls+filetype%3Axls" target="_blank"><code><strong>waterfalls filetype:xls</strong></code></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><code><strong>ext:</strong></code></td>\r\n<td>Same as <code><strong>filetype:</strong></code></td>\r\n<td><code><strong><a href="https://www.google.com.ua/search?q=waterfalls+ext%3Axls" target="_blank">waterfalls ext:xls</a></strong></code></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><code><strong>inurl:</strong></code></td>\r\n<td>Search in URLs.</td>\r\n<td><a href="https://www.google.com.ua/search?q=inurl%3Asvg" target="_blank"><code><strong>inurl:svg</strong></code></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><code><strong>allintitle:</strong></code></td>\r\n<td>Search in page titles.</td>\r\n<td><a href="https://www.google.com.ua/search?q=allintitle%3A&quot;nike&quot;+running" target="_blank"><code><strong><b>allintitle:"nike" running</b></strong></code></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><code><strong>allintext:</strong></code></td>\r\n<td>Search all words in body text (not links or page title).</td>\r\n<td><a href="https://www.google.com.ua/search?q=allintext%3Anorth+pole" target="_blank"><code><strong><b>allintext:north pole</b></strong></code></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><code><strong>allinanchor:</strong></code></td>\r\n<td>Search in anchors (links) on a page</td>\r\n<td><code><strong><a href="http://www.google.com/search?q=allinanchor:+best+museums+sydney" target="_blank">allinanchor: best museums sydney</a></strong></code></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><code><strong>intext:</strong></code></t