html intitle:"index of" apk</a></code></li>\r\n	<li>Specify the words are close to each other in the text\r\n<code><a href="https://www.google.com.ua/search?q=ipad+AROUND(2)+wi-fi" target="_blank">ipad AROUND(2) wi-fi</a></code></li>\r\n	<li>Search for faces on Images, add to URL:\r\n<code>&amp;imgtype=face</code></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div><em>source: <a href="http://lifehacker.com/top-10-clever-google-search-tricks-1450186165" target="_blank">Top 10 Clever Google Search Tricks</a></em></div>\r\n<em>source: <a href="http://www.marcandangel.com/2007/07/25/7-clever-google-tricks-worth-knowing/" target="_blank">7 Clever Google Tricks Worth Knowing</a></em>', 'Google Search Help', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '791-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-08 17:36:21', '2015-04-08 17:36:21', '', 791, 'http://pcadvice.co.nf/blog/791-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
